    "causal_summary": "The sk-improve-agent skill evaluates agents by checking **keyword presence in markdown** (~15-20% of what a true agent improvement system needs). The scorer tests \"does the file mention `spec.md`?\" rather than \"does the agent understand spec folders?\". The benchmark tests \"does output have required headings?\" rather than \"is the output correct and useful?\".",
